Wednesday September 03, 2008.

Alex welcomes singer-songwriter, spoken word artist, author and actor Henry Rollins to talk about censorship.  Alex also talks with economist and journalist F. William Engdahl, author of A Century of War: Anglo-American Oil Politics and the New World Order.

Sourced from the Infowars live stream or the podcast.  Contains the behind the scenes discussion during commercial breaks.  Four hours duration before commercial edit takes it to just over 3 hours of playing time.  
